device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OPTBSV:Ophthalmic Tomography B-scan Volume Analysis
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OPTENF:Ophthalmic Tomography En Face
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OPV:Ophthalmic Visual Field
